text: Maryorie Nicole Pérez Rodríguez (born 25 November 1997) is a Panamanian footballer who plays as a defender for the Panama women's national team. ==International career== Pérez appeared in one match for Panama at the 2018 CONCACAF Women's Championship. ==References== Category:1997 births Category:Living people Category:Panamanian women's footballers Category:Panama women's international footballers Category:Women's association football defenders
